---
title: Puerto Rican-Style Sazón Chicken & Rice with Dark Meat Chicken & Cilantro
description: This Hispanic Heritage Month, take your taste buds on a delicious journey with this classic Puerto Rican–style meal! You’ll season dark meat chicken with bold sazón seasoning (cumin, achiote, coriander, garlic, oregano), then sauté to juicy perfection with onion, pepper, and garlic. Add rice, then simmer it all together for a hearty, homestyle one-pan dish that hits all the right notes.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66ccac5f86da4647f4e36768-2f30733b.jpeg
